<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Betwixt" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Betwixt,</orth> prepos., of the same use as between (in R3 Qq usually <emph>betwixt,</emph> Ff. <emph>between</emph>).<lb />1) <cit><quote>b. twelve and one,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 4.1.85" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado IV, 1, 85</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>each soil b. that Holmedon and this seat of ours,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.1.65" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 1, 65</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.1.52" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 1, 52</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 1.3.45" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A I, 3, 45</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.3.49" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 3, 49</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 4.2.44" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 44</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 3.7.48" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 III, 7, 48</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 3.2.29" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. III, 2, 29</bibl> etc. Idea of hinderance: <cit><quote>I will stand b. you and danger,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 2.2.66" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. II, 2, 66</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>set bounds b. their love and me,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 4.1.21" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 1, 21</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>thou keepest the stroke b. thy begging and my meditation,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 4.2.119" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 119</bibl></cit>.
<lb />2) <cit><quote>just the difference b. the constant red and mingled damask,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 3.5.123" default="NO" valid="yes">As III, 5, 123</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. aww 1.3.116" default="NO" valid="yes">All's I, 3, 116</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 1.1.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. I, 1, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 2.1.87" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 87</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 3.1.220" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A III, 1, 220</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.4.82" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 4, 82</bibl> etc.
<lb />3) <cit><quote>b. mine eye and heart a league is took,</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 47.1" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 47, 1</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. mm 5.218" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. V, 218</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 1.1.62" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado I, 1, 62</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 1.1.84" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. I, 1, 84</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 4.3.141" default="NO" valid="yes">As IV, 3, 141</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 1.1.25" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. I, 1, 25</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 1.1.50" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 1, 50</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 3.1.12" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 12</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 5.1.73" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 73</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 5.5.10" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A V, 5, 10</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.1.106" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 1, 106</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.1.139" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 139</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 3.1.139" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 139</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.1.96" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 96</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.1.96" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 96</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.4.99" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 4, 99</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.1.73" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 1, 73</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.37" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 3, 37</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 1.1.180" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 I, 1, 180</bibl> etc.
<lb />4) <cit><quote>share the advice b. you,</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 2.1.3" default="NO" valid="yes">All's II, 1, 3</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>things known b. us three,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.571" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 571</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>b. ourselves let us decide it then,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.1.119" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A IV, 1, 119</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>